     ( iv )       \{image("BDH_3.3.11.png",width=>250,height=>250)\} 
$ECENTER
$PAR
Sketch, on paper, the \(x(t)\)- and \(y(t)\)-graphs for the solutions corresponding to the initial conditions specified below
